flowchart TB
    Client([Client App])
    Catalog[Catalog Service<br/>metadata]
    CDN[(Audio Storage / CDN<br/>multi-bitrate + DRM)]
    Recs[Recommendation Service<br/>weekly playlist + radio]
    Events[(Play Events Stream<br/>partitioned)]
    Royalty[Royalty Pipeline<br/>aggregator + payout]
    Models[(Embeddings + CF Models<br/>offline trained)]

    Client --> Catalog
    Client -->|stream chunks| CDN
    Client --> Recs
    Client -.->|behaviour events| Events
    Events --> Royalty
    Events -.-> Models
    Models --> Recs
    Catalog --> Recs

